==影響==
特朗普主義不單獲得白人的支持，美國的黑人、拉丁裔和亞裔群體間都有支持者，美國國外亦出現了具規模的特朗普主義擁護者或團體，例如日本的[[網絡右翼|網絡右翼]]<ref name="asahi trumpism">{{Cite|last=木下|first=ちがや|url=https://webronza.asahi.com/politics/articles/2020121900003.html|title=限界ネトウヨと右翼ヘゲモニーの終焉|work=[[朝日新聞|朝日]]論座|language=ja|date=2020-12-22|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313033101/https://webronza.asahi.com/politics/articles/2020121900003.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和新興宗教[[幸福科學|幸福科學]]等<ref name=wapojapan>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/07/trump-qanon-stop-the-steal-japan/|title=Trump’s ‘stop the steal’ message finds an international audience among conspiracy theorists and suspected cults|date=2021-01-07|accessdate=2021-01-08|work=華盛頓郵報|last=Taylor|first=Adam|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113010400/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/07/trump-qanon-stop-the-steal-japan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

